 ######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

start_at = far_1_tavern
start_theme = my_theme
themes {
   my_theme : theme {
      theme_settings {
         losegame_jingle = on
         success_jingle  = on
         wingame_jingle  = on
         failure_jingle  = off
      }
   }
}
######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################
loading_screen = pixel_templedao
on_startup {
   
   : print "This is a text based adventure game. Type in commands to perform actions, solve pussles and progress the story.\n TIPS \n -typing 'EXAMINE' followed by an object name usually provides more info on that object \n -typing 'INVENTORY' shows you a list of things you are currently carrying \n -typing 'SAVE' saves your game \n -typing 'LOAD' will load a saved game";
   : press_any_key ;
   : ask_string question = "Before we begin...What is your name?"  var = "name" ;
   
}
######################################
#  Strings                           #
######################################

strings {
   
   name : string "" ;
   
}
######################################
#  Locations                         #
######################################

locations {

   far_1_tavern : location "" ;
   far_2_tavern : location "" ;
   outside_tavern : location "" ;
   inside_tavern : location "" ;
   toilet : location "" ;
   chamber : location "" layout = "H G D X O"  ;
   
}

######################################
#  Connections                       #
######################################

connections {

   from, direction, to = [
     // outside_apothecary, north, road_1,
     // apothecary, north, road_2, 
     // far_1_tavern, north, far_2_tavern, 
     // far_2_tavern, north, outside_tavern, 
     
     inside_tavern, enter, chamber, 
      ]
   
}

######################################
#  Objects                           #
######################################

objects {
   
   painting : scenery "a haunting painting" ;
  // stools : scenery "typical bar stools" ;
   cloak_woman : scenery "a woman in a cloak" at = "inside_tavern" conspicuous = "false"  ; 
   bartender : scenery "the bartender";
   ancient_key : object "an ancient key" ;
   red_drink : object "a red drink" ;
   blue_drink : object "a blue drink" ;
   green_drink : object "a green drink" ;
   yellow_drink : object "a yellow drink" ;
   purple_drink : object "a purple drink" ;
   incense : object "a stick of incense" ;
   candle : scenery "a burning candle" ;
   table_words : scenery "legible words seared into the table from the flames" ;
   empty_seat : scenery "empty seat now that the woman has left" conspicuous = "false" ;
   keyhole_1 : scenery "keyhole on the painting";
   chaos : scenery "the table of Chaos" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"   ;
   logic : scenery "the table of Logic" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   order : scenery "the table of Order" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   structure : scenery "the table of Structure" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   mystery : scenery "the table of Mystery" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   guardian : scenery "a guardian watching over us" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   
   
}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {
  
//describe far from tavern
      : if (is_at "far_1_tavern") {
      : print "You open your eyes. The surrounding looks unfamiliar. It is nighttime." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "The air is curiously still and fills your mouth with a stale taste.  It’s too quiet, and not a single creature of the night stirs. The only thing breaking the silence is the incessant ringing in your ears..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "“What happened? Where is this place?" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Darkness seeps out of the night. You can see nothing except...a faint glow to the north \n Looks like you have no choice but to walk towards it" ;
      }
      
//describe far from tavern
      : if (is_at "far_2_tavern") {
      : print "You're getting closer to the glow. You can make out an outline of a building of some sort." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "You sigh with relief...at least there is civilisation here. Better keep walking" ;
      }  
      
//describe outside tavern
      : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : print "You seem to be standing in front of a door leading into what looks like an apothecarium..or is it a tavern? " ;
      }
   
//describe inside tavern
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
         : if (is_present "cloak_woman") {
         : print "You look around and start to wonder what kind of room you are even in. To your right, you notice a PAINTING hanging on the wall. To your left, a bar. A narrow door at the back probably leads to the BATHROOM.";
         : print "A WOMAN in a cloak is sitting at the bar. She is drinking a shimmery beverage. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the bar. The shelf behind the bar is filled with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and a lot of things you don’t have a word for.";
       
         }
         : if (is_chamber_open == true) {
         : print "A whole other chamber was hidden behind the painting" ;
         : play_music sound="ambient_chant";
         }
         
         : if (is_present "empty_seat") {
         : print "A narrow door at the back probably leads to the BATHROOM. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the bar. The shelf behind the bar is filled with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and a lot of things you don’t have a word for.";
         }
         : if (entered_toilet > 0 && has_not_created "table_words" ) {
         : print "...you notice a small TABLE under the painting. Was that there before?..."; 
         }
      }
   
//describe inside toilet
      : if (is_at "toilet") {
         : print "a regular bathroom stall. Complete with a sink, toilet bowl and lots of scribblings on the wall";
         
      }

//dweling chamber
      
      : if (is_at "chamber") {
         : print "You enter the chamber. The sounds are soothing to your ears and the lingering smoke of burned incense fills your nostrils.\n Your eyes gaze upon five TABLES in the middle of the room, each boldly displaying a unique colour and insignia - CHAOS red, LOGIC blue, ORDER yellow, STRUCTURE green, and MYSTERY purple \n To your immediate left you notice a cloaked mysterious figure watching over everyone. Is he a GUARDIAN?" ;
      }
      

}

######################################
#  Booleans                          
######################################

booleans {
   
   is_key_exists : boolean;
   is_intro_done : boolean;
  // is_sitting : boolean;
   is_incense_there : boolean;
   is_quest_started : boolean;
   is_woman_ready : boolean;
   is_woman_intro_done : boolean;
   is_heard_something : boolean;
   is_chamber_open : boolean;
   is_clean : boolean;
   is_chamber_quest : boolean;
   is_asked_work : boolean;
   is_asked_future : boolean;
   
 
}



######################################
#  Integers                          #
######################################

integers {
   
   question_1 : integer "0" ;
   drinking : integer "0" ;
   drunkeness : integer "0" ;
   toilet_writing : integer "0" ;
   entered_toilet : integer "0" ;
   quest_counter : integer "0" ;
   impostor_try : integer "3" ;
   
}



######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################

barriers {
   
   chamber : block {
      location = chamber
      block_when_not = is_chamber_open
   }
   
}

######################################
#  Subroutines                       #
######################################

subroutines {
//game over
   end_game : subroutine {
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : print "YOU DIED" ;
      : failure ;
      : lose_game;
         }
 //game over at impostor       
end_game2 : subroutine {
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : print "YOU FAILED" ;
      : failure ;
      : lose_game;
         }

//woman questions
   woman_questions : subroutine {
      : add_choice "You need to post your feet pictures to the devs"  {
      : print "<'I have *sniff*...and now...my feet is all over feetfinder.com! waaaaaaaa! <6>>" ;
      }
      : add_choice "You need to verify yourself in voice chat"  {
      : print "<You kidding me? I was in there for ages. Then I got told dat is not da way to get verified!<6>>" ;
      }
      : add_choice "You just need to react with an emoji"  {
      : print "<'What? First I've heard if this. React where?<6>>" ;
            : add_choice "On the announcements channel"  {
            : print "<Liar. I've seen many reactions on that channel. None of them worked<6>>" ;
            }
            : add_choice "On one of the pinned messages in the verification channel"  {
            : print "<Oh! I've not thought to check the pinned messages. Which emoji do I use?<6>>" ;
                  : add_choice "The thumbs up emoji"  {
                  : print "<You sure? Hmm, ok I will try that right away!<6>>" ;
                  : print "She thanks you one last time and leaves. \n You secretly hope you told her the right thing..." ;
                  : success ;
                  : destroy "cloak_woman" ;
                  }
                  : add_choice "The sun emoji"  {
                  : print "<You sure? Hmm, ok I will try that right away!<6>>" ;
                  : print "She thanks you one last time and leaves. \n You secretly hope you told her the right thing..." ;
                  : success ;
                  : destroy "cloak_woman" ;
                  }
                   : add_choice "The fire emoji"  {
                  : print "<You sure? Hmm, ok I will try that right away!<6>>" ;
                  : print "She thanks you one last time and leaves. \n You secretly hope you told her the right thing..." ;  
                  : success ;
                  : destroy "cloak_woman" ;
                  }
                  : choose "you ponder her words for a moment...and respond with" ;
                  : create "empty_seat";
                  : increment "quest_counter" ;
                  
            }
            : add_choice "On the voice-verify channel"  {
            : print "<I'm starting to wonder if you know what you are talking about. You can't use emojis in voice channels...<6>>" ;
            }
            
            : choose "you ponder her words for a moment...and respond with" ;
            : press_any_key ;
            : redescribe;
            
      }
      : choose "you ponder her words for a moment...and respond with" ; 
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      : done ;
          
   }

//red table
chaos_s : subroutine {
     : print "You approach the red table. There are two templars sitting there, wearing robes with a 'Chaos' insignia.\n They are the loudest templars in the room, scheming loudly about 'trolling fudders', 'creating more memes' and... 'eating beans?'. These bros know how to party!";
     : if (is_chamber_quest == true) {
        : add_choice "What are you working on?"  {
           : print "<Chaos Templar 1: 'Just working on the next article for the Temple Codex/Newsletter'<2>>" ;
           : print "<Chaos Templar 2: 'Oh...err...just some marketing stuff...'<2>>" ;
        }
         : add_choice "What's in the pipeline?"  {
           : print "<Chaos Templar 1: 'Educational materials for the protocol!'<2>>" ;
           : print "<Chaos Templar 2: 'umm...poker night?'<2>>" ;
        }
        : choose "You think for a moment, and decide to ask the table" ;
     }
     
}


//blue table
logic_s : subroutine {
     : print "You approach the blue table. There are two Templars at this table today. Their robe has a bright blue 'Logic' insignia, though this is not the only thing that caught your eye… \n One of the templars is fidgeting with his hand, cracking knuckles… is he nervous or just deep in thought?";
      : if (is_chamber_quest == true) {
        : add_choice "What are you working on?"  {
           : print "<Logic Templar 1: 'Shhhh! I almost cracked the code on sustainable yield...'<9>>" ;
           : print "<Logic Templar 2: 'Faith mechanics is my top priority'<9>>" ; 
        }
         : add_choice "What's in the pipeline?"  {
           : print "<Logic Templar 1: 'Quit disturbing me! I duno, there are a whole heap of analytics and calculators I need to create<9>>" ;
           : print "<Logic Templar 2: 'It's all about the treasury investment opportunities baby!''<9>>" ;
        }
        : choose "You think for a moment, and decide to ask the table" ;
     }
}

     }
}
